headline: Gold prices, BioNTech to acquire CureVac, Tapestry upgrade
summary: Yahoo Finance host Josh Lipton tracks today's top moving stocks and biggest market stories in this Market Minute, including gold prices (GC=F) moving up on President Trump's latest trade tariff plans, BioNTech's (BNTX) acquisition of German rival CureVac (CVAC), and TD Cowen's upgrade on Tapestry (TPR). Stay up to date on the latest market action, minute-by-minute, with Yahoo Finance's Market Minute.
